---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About The Cache"
  description="The Cache is a weekly curation of the best gear, tech, fashion, and finds for men. Every pick is independently researched — nothing is paid for."
>
  <article style="max-width:640px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-family:Georgia,serif;">About The Cache</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--brand-muted); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:2rem;"><em>The best stuff you didn't know you needed.</em></p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What we are</h2>
    <p>The Cache is a weekly curation publication for men who care about quality. Every week we surface the top 5 across gear, tech, style, cars, and drinks — things that are genuinely worth your attention, not whatever brand has the biggest ad budget.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">The rule</h2>
    <p>Nothing gets into The Cache because someone paid for it. Every recommendation is independently selected based on one question: <em>is this actually worth it?</em> Affiliate links are used transparently — we earn a commission if you buy, at no cost to you. Sponsored content is clearly labeled and kept separate.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What you get</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.25rem; color:var(--brand-muted);">
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Weekly email</strong> — 5 picks across gear, tech, style, cars, and drinks</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Product deep dives</strong> — long-form reviews on the site for things worth a closer look</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Seasonal drops</strong> — quarterly "Cache Drop" with the best seasonal finds</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="subscribe-bar" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      <h2>Get the weekly drop.</h2>
      <p>Free. Independent. Unsubscribe any time.</p>
      <div class="subscribe-form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" aria-label="Email address" />
        <button class="btn">Subscribe</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
